<tr>
    <td style="min-width: 200px; max-width: 200px;">
        <p><small><b data-bind="text: Name"></b></small></p>
        <img data-bind="attr:{src:ImageUrl, alt:Name}" width="109" />
    </td>
    <td style="min-width: 130px; max-width: 130px;">
        <p data-bind="text: BalanceTransferText"></p>
    </td>
    <td style="min-width: 80px; max-width: 80px;">
        <p data-bind="text: IntroBalanceTfrFee + '% fee'"></p>
    </td>
    <td style="text-align: center;">
        <p><b data-bind="text: SavingAmount() > 0 ? '£' + SavingAmount() : '--'"></b></p>
    </td>
    <td style="text-align: center;">
        <p><b data-bind="text: Score() > 0 ? Score() : '?'"></b></p>
    </td>
    <td style="padding-top: 45px;">
        <a class="btn btn-warning">Apply Now</a>
    </td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td colspan="8">
        <small>
            <b>Representative Example: </b>If you spend &#163;<span data-bind="text: RepresentativeExampleCreditLimit"></span> at a purchase interest rate of
            <span data-bind="text: RepresentativeAPR"></span>% (variable) your Representative APR will be <span data-bind="text: BalanceTransferAER"></span>% (variable)
            @*<span data-bind="visible: AnnualFee() > 0">with an annual fee of &#163;<span data-bind="text: AnnualFee"></span></span>.*@
        </small>
    </td>
</tr>